1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.200
Tell me when I can start.

2
00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.760
You can start.

3
00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:07.920
You can start now.

4
00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:10.200
OK.

5
00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:12.360
Good evening, everyone.

6
00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:13.920
I'm Christine Hage.

7
00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:17.240
I'm born in France from Polish parents.

8
00:00:17.240 --> 00:00:21.560
So I have stories about France, about Poland.

9
00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:25.520
And I'm living happily in Vienna, Austria,

10
00:00:25.520 --> 00:00:32.920
because Shwemataji gave me a lovely, strong Austrian husband.

11
00:00:32.920 --> 00:00:42.480
So during my first India tour in 85, 86, it was in Raurie.

12
00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:45.880
I heard for the first time the Mahalakshmi's totem.

13
00:00:48.760 --> 00:00:54.800
I don't remember if it was a music program or during a puja.

14
00:00:54.840 --> 00:01:01.440
But when I heard this song for the first time, I mean, I was so moved.

15
00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:08.200
I was blasted and I started to cry, to cry.

16
00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:12.280
And in myself, I said, but why are you crying?

17
00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:15.160
Shwemataji is here and you are crying.

18
00:01:15.160 --> 00:01:20.800
And I looked at Shwemataji and she was crying too.

19
00:01:20.800 --> 00:01:24.000
And at the end of the song, she said,

20
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:30.000
you see, it doesn't matter if you are singing or if you are listening.

21
00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:34.160
When you feel the spirit, we are one.

22
00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:37.920
And for this, also session with stories.

23
00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:41.720
Doesn't matter who speaks or who listens.

24
00:01:41.720 --> 00:01:46.280
But these stories, I mean, they are so fascinating

25
00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:52.280
because they show the divine play, how Shwemataji.

26
00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:56.880
For each one of us, and we are thousands,

27
00:01:56.880 --> 00:02:04.080
created situations for every one of us to learn something about ourselves,

28
00:02:04.080 --> 00:02:07.280
to go deeper in spirituality.

29
00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:11.800
And we such love, such care, such humor also.

30
00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:17.800
And only the divine can manage such show.

31
00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:28.640
So I met Shwemataji for the first time in August 82 in Lausanne, in Switzerland.

32
00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:34.040
I saw I was by chance there and I saw the poster of Shwemataji.

33
00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:39.160
She was not the motherly face on this poster.

34
00:02:39.160 --> 00:02:41.680
It was the guru face.

35
00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:45.560
I looked at her and I said, oh, I know her.

36
00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:51.680
She's strict, but I need someone strict to make order in my life.

37
00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:53.880
And I went to the program.

38
00:02:53.880 --> 00:03:00.320
I was staying completely behind because I didn't want to be enrolled in a set.

39
00:03:00.320 --> 00:03:04.360
So I observed everyone who was there.

40
00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:08.000
And I saw at this time, Marie Martin was pregnant.

41
00:03:08.040 --> 00:03:16.400
And I said to myself, oh, we can also get children when we do this yoga.

42
00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:25.440
And Shwemataji came a little bit later, I mean, maybe 30 or 45 minutes.

43
00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:31.680
She came and she was just walking majestically in her white siren.

44
00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:42.640
Suddenly, a couple of Swiss people stood up and showed her the watch because she was too late and we are in Switzerland.

45
00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:51.800
And Shwemataji just went on and she said, for God, there is no time.

46
00:03:51.800 --> 00:03:54.840
Just to hear this, I said, she's the right one.

47
00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:57.160
She is sent by God.

48
00:03:57.160 --> 00:04:11.760
And after the realization, I mean, I just felt so strong vibrations and this confirmed what I was looking for all the time,

49
00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:20.760
even when I was a child, because my name, Christine, there is Christ inside and I'm born in Pankot,

50
00:04:20.760 --> 00:04:29.760
Kingston, and I knew I will once feel like the apostles, the Holy Ghost on my head.

51
00:04:29.760 --> 00:04:33.080
And this was the time.

52
00:04:33.080 --> 00:04:37.360
Shwemataji left the hall and I stayed in the hall.

53
00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:40.120
I was alone. I couldn't go away.

54
00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:43.640
And suddenly she was near me.

55
00:04:43.640 --> 00:04:47.960
She took my hands and she said, did you feel it?

56
00:04:47.960 --> 00:04:51.200
And I just could answer, yes.

57
00:04:51.200 --> 00:05:01.120
And I felt as I don't know, I cannot describe what I felt, but like an energy, something that she gave me.

58
00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:05.120
So I came back to Moulouse, to France.

59
00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:09.840
I gave realization to some friends, to some relatives.

60
00:05:09.840 --> 00:05:13.440
And we were a little group meeting every week to meditate.

61
00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:20.200
And with the help of the Swiss yogis.

62
00:05:20.200 --> 00:05:26.560
And this was, I met Shwemataji in 82, August 82.

63
00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:35.240
In Easter 83, my friend Martin and me, we were teaching both of them.

64
00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:36.480
We had holidays.

65
00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:43.760
So we went to the ashram in Le Fournet at this time.

66
00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:49.040
And for the first time, I entered a meditation room.

67
00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:55.360
And this was also overwhelming to see all these pictures of mother.

68
00:05:55.360 --> 00:06:01.360
And I remember I just sat down and I spoke to Shwemataji.

69
00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:13.520
I told her, please come in my town also to give realization to such a lot of seekers there.

70
00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:25.480
In June 83, the five ladies from the province, from Moulouse, we went to Paris where Shwemataji gave programs in Paris.

71
00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:29.240
When we were at the airport, Shwemataji came.

72
00:06:29.240 --> 00:06:36.600
And from the group of the five ladies, I was the only one to have seen Shwemataji physically.

73
00:06:36.600 --> 00:06:40.080
The other one just was on the picture.

74
00:06:40.080 --> 00:06:46.720
And one told me she was expecting a princess or a queen to come.

75
00:06:46.720 --> 00:06:55.560
And Shwemataji came just with a coat, with a scarf on her head like a normal lady.

76
00:06:55.560 --> 00:07:02.760
And when she saw us, she said, why are you looking so serious all of you?

77
00:07:02.760 --> 00:07:12.240
Thinking about your catches, about your problems, are you not happy to see your mother?

78
00:07:12.240 --> 00:07:13.480
And she left.

79
00:07:13.480 --> 00:07:18.320
And we didn't know where she's going to the flood of Mary or to the ashram.

80
00:07:18.320 --> 00:07:21.400
So we decided to go to the ashram.

81
00:07:21.400 --> 00:07:23.560
We just knew the direction.

82
00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:28.240
We knew it's leurancy, but no address.

83
00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:29.120
We went there.

84
00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:30.520
We were in this place.

85
00:07:30.520 --> 00:07:36.120
And suddenly we saw a house and a lot of shoes outside.

86
00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:40.760
So we said, OK, it must be there.

87
00:07:40.760 --> 00:07:43.000
So we enter the house.

88
00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:48.800
And there was at this time not a lot of yogis, maybe 10.

89
00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:53.200
And Shwemataji sitting in her armchair.

90
00:07:53.240 --> 00:07:56.560
And the leader at this time said, come, come, come.

91
00:07:56.560 --> 00:08:00.160
And I just came in front of Shwemataji.

92
00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:02.280
I did namaste.

93
00:08:02.280 --> 00:08:07.360
And he said, Shwemataji, this is Christine from Moulouse.

94
00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:11.360
And she said, but I know her.

95
00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:15.480
And she did like this to me, to come to her.

96
00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:16.600
She took me.

97
00:08:16.600 --> 00:08:18.560
She embraced me.

98
00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:22.840
And she said, you are meeting again after 2000 years.

99
00:08:22.880 --> 00:08:27.960
She confirmed what I was feeling already as a child,

100
00:08:27.960 --> 00:08:32.120
that I was living in the time of Christ.

101
00:08:32.120 --> 00:08:36.520
At the program, she did a program, evening program.

102
00:08:36.520 --> 00:08:38.760
And at the end of the program, she

103
00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:42.400
asked the yogis to come in front to help her

104
00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:44.800
to work on the new people.

105
00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:49.520
We from the province, we didn't know how to work on someone.

106
00:08:49.520 --> 00:08:52.360
We didn't want to do something wrong.

107
00:08:52.400 --> 00:08:57.000
So we stayed completely behind in the hole.

108
00:08:57.000 --> 00:09:02.520
Someone came and gave me the coat of Shwemataji to hold.

109
00:09:02.520 --> 00:09:06.400
Such vibrations coming out of this coat.

110
00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:10.200
And all the five ladies, I mean, we

111
00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:14.160
were feeling a little bit, how to say,

112
00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:21.600
Schuldig guilty that we couldn't help Shwemataji.

113
00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:26.400
But I tell you, we were just in total awareness

114
00:09:26.400 --> 00:09:27.360
at this moment.

115
00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:32.920
We were just looking at her, so happy to see her.

116
00:09:32.920 --> 00:09:35.720
Shwemataji finished her session.

117
00:09:35.720 --> 00:09:39.800
Someone took again away the coat of Shwemataji.

118
00:09:39.800 --> 00:09:41.240
And she left the hole.

119
00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:47.080
But when she passed near her, near us,

120
00:09:47.080 --> 00:09:51.320
a little group of the five ladies, she stopped.

121
00:09:51.320 --> 00:09:55.520
And she said, she did namaste, and she said,

122
00:09:55.520 --> 00:09:57.280
thank you very much.

123
00:09:57.280 --> 00:10:02.960
You have no idea how much you helped me this evening.

124
00:10:02.960 --> 00:10:04.880
Thank you very much.

125
00:10:04.880 --> 00:10:08.600
And this is pure Zen, action in inaction.

126
00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:13.600
So this was in June.

127
00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:21.280
And our first puja in a foreign country

128
00:10:21.280 --> 00:10:26.280
was in England, Guru Puja in Lajjil.

129
00:10:26.280 --> 00:10:31.560
And the 24th of July.

130
00:10:31.560 --> 00:10:34.280
Oh, wait.

131
00:10:34.280 --> 00:10:37.080
Before I have to tell you, I want

132
00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:42.880
before I have to tell you that when

133
00:10:42.880 --> 00:10:45.520
I was in the ashram of Switzerland,

134
00:10:45.520 --> 00:10:48.920
I forgot to tell you that I meditate.

135
00:10:48.920 --> 00:10:52.280
I asked Shwemataji to come to our place.

136
00:10:52.280 --> 00:10:56.840
And after this, when I came out of the meditation room,

137
00:10:56.840 --> 00:11:01.040
Arno told me, the leader at this time told me,

138
00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:05.960
you see, Christine, Shwemataji's tour is already planned.

139
00:11:05.960 --> 00:11:10.520
But write an invitation to her.

140
00:11:10.520 --> 00:11:13.600
It might be that she's coming to Melus.

141
00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:19.240
So with Martin and with our poor English,

142
00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:24.320
we just wrote a little, little letter just

143
00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:28.920
to thank Shwemataji to have given us the realization

144
00:11:28.920 --> 00:11:34.840
that now we know the meaning of the word love, friendship,

145
00:11:34.840 --> 00:11:37.720
and we would like her to come to give realization

146
00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:41.200
to the seekers of our place.

147
00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:46.480
And in Lajjil, the 24th of July, this

148
00:11:46.480 --> 00:11:51.440
was the day of Holy Christine, Naman's Day.

149
00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:56.400
Yeah, the day Arno came to me and he said, Christine,

150
00:11:56.400 --> 00:11:59.880
Shwemataji is coming to Melus.

151
00:11:59.880 --> 00:12:03.160
And she came the 1st of September,

152
00:12:03.160 --> 00:12:07.440
the birthday of my sister.

153
00:12:07.440 --> 00:12:12.960
I mean, this detail, this coincidence.

154
00:12:12.960 --> 00:12:20.120
And she came and we were first in Switzerland

155
00:12:20.120 --> 00:12:21.400
for the Krishna puja.

156
00:12:21.400 --> 00:12:25.760
And we were not a lot of maybe 20, 25 people.

157
00:12:25.760 --> 00:12:28.600
It was in the garden of the ashram.

158
00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:33.880
And after we, Miss Martin, we left quickly to Melus

159
00:12:33.880 --> 00:12:38.040
to prepare my flat for Shwemataji's coming.

160
00:12:38.040 --> 00:12:40.960
In my bedroom, there was a cupboard.

161
00:12:40.960 --> 00:12:45.720
And on this cupboard, there was such a lot of spots.

162
00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:49.720
I wanted to get rid of these spots to clean.

163
00:12:49.720 --> 00:12:54.520
And I took chemical things, you see, to clean.

164
00:12:54.520 --> 00:12:57.080
Nothing went away.

165
00:12:57.080 --> 00:13:00.040
And after some time, I say, OK, I gave up.

166
00:13:00.040 --> 00:13:04.920
I just took a little chiffon to the last chance

167
00:13:04.920 --> 00:13:08.040
to put away the dust.

168
00:13:08.040 --> 00:13:12.480
And suddenly, all the spots disappeared by themselves.

169
00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:17.840
But in the same moment, Martin was in the kitchen cleaning

170
00:13:17.840 --> 00:13:20.000
the candle holder.

171
00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:24.840
And she shouted, Christine, what is happening?

172
00:13:24.840 --> 00:13:30.040
The candle holders are cleaning by themselves.

173
00:13:30.040 --> 00:13:35.080
And later on, yeah, we were told that already the Ghanas

174
00:13:35.080 --> 00:13:38.400
and the deities were in this place

175
00:13:38.400 --> 00:13:42.720
to help us to prepare Shwemataji's coming.

176
00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:49.400
Shwemataji came from Basel to Melus by train.

177
00:13:49.400 --> 00:13:53.800
And we organized an armchair, comfort table

178
00:13:53.840 --> 00:13:54.960
that we rented.

179
00:13:54.960 --> 00:13:57.440
We put some saris on.

180
00:13:57.440 --> 00:14:01.240
But we forgot, completely forgot,

181
00:14:01.240 --> 00:14:07.360
to prepare a table for her food when she was eating.

182
00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:13.240
Can you imagine Shwemataji had her plate, warm plate,

183
00:14:13.240 --> 00:14:18.280
on her lap to eat because there was no table?

184
00:14:18.280 --> 00:14:21.520
And Warren, who was with Shwemataji,

185
00:14:21.560 --> 00:14:25.080
was so cross with Martin as we me.

186
00:14:25.080 --> 00:14:29.360
How would we dare not to sing about this?

187
00:14:29.360 --> 00:14:31.240
I mean, he was really tough.

188
00:14:31.240 --> 00:14:34.720
So we got a little bit of fright.

189
00:14:34.720 --> 00:14:39.760
So I went to my neighbor to hold, to take a table.

190
00:14:39.760 --> 00:14:43.760
And I came back with a table, a little table.

191
00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:48.760
And Shwemataji, when she saw the table, she said, no, no, no,

192
00:14:48.760 --> 00:14:49.320
no.

193
00:14:49.320 --> 00:14:51.720
I don't need any table.

194
00:14:51.720 --> 00:14:54.520
I'm completely satisfied.

195
00:14:54.520 --> 00:14:57.160
You see, I could have eaten in the train.

196
00:14:57.160 --> 00:15:02.120
But I said, no, I want to eat in Melus.

197
00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:08.160
I mean, this delicacy of her not to hurt her.

198
00:15:08.160 --> 00:15:12.200
And also, she was asking me the permission

199
00:15:12.200 --> 00:15:17.920
to use my telephone to phone to her husband in England.

200
00:15:17.920 --> 00:15:20.040
She asked the permission.

201
00:15:20.040 --> 00:15:21.760
The other yogis didn't.

202
00:15:21.760 --> 00:15:23.720
They just took the phone and phoned.

203
00:15:26.280 --> 00:15:29.800
And she did the program.

204
00:15:29.800 --> 00:15:34.320
And at the end of the program, suddenly she said,

205
00:15:34.320 --> 00:15:37.080
how is it that I'm here in Melus?

206
00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:38.960
It was not planned.

207
00:15:38.960 --> 00:15:43.080
It's only the desire of one woman who said.

208
00:15:43.080 --> 00:15:47.200
And she repeated exactly the sentences

209
00:15:47.200 --> 00:15:51.280
that I said in the meditation room in Switzerland.

210
00:15:51.280 --> 00:15:56.400
And only me, I could understand this.

211
00:15:56.400 --> 00:15:59.400
And history, I repeated history.

212
00:15:59.400 --> 00:16:03.760
I told history also in the 90s when

213
00:16:03.760 --> 00:16:08.320
we were in Poland to start Saja Yoga in Poland.

214
00:16:08.320 --> 00:16:13.440
Because Annegret and me, we were just both of us

215
00:16:13.440 --> 00:16:17.280
to do the programs twice a week.

216
00:16:17.280 --> 00:16:19.920
And the people were asking, do you

217
00:16:19.920 --> 00:16:23.960
think Śwematajik will come once to Poland?

218
00:16:23.960 --> 00:16:28.640
We are such an incipient country.

219
00:16:28.640 --> 00:16:32.840
And they were hesitating.

220
00:16:32.840 --> 00:16:34.920
And I told them the story.

221
00:16:34.920 --> 00:16:39.000
I said, look, when it was a desire of one woman,

222
00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:43.280
we are here 200, 250.

223
00:16:43.280 --> 00:16:48.480
If we have the desire, Śwematajik will come.

224
00:16:48.480 --> 00:16:52.960
And Annegret also said, and let's give abandon.

225
00:16:52.960 --> 00:16:57.520
And about abandon, Śwematajik also in Poland, in Warsaw,

226
00:16:57.520 --> 00:17:01.560
gave us the meaning of abandon.

227
00:17:01.560 --> 00:17:05.440
Because we told her that people were queuing so

228
00:17:05.440 --> 00:17:06.680
that we work on them.

229
00:17:06.680 --> 00:17:08.560
We were just both of them.

230
00:17:08.560 --> 00:17:13.480
So we couldn't spend a lot of time to work on each one.

231
00:17:13.480 --> 00:17:18.280
So either it was cool and it was OK, and it was warm.

232
00:17:18.280 --> 00:17:20.120
So we just gave abandon.

233
00:17:20.120 --> 00:17:23.160
And people asked us, what are you doing?

234
00:17:23.160 --> 00:17:26.960
And we said, we are phoning to God without wire.

235
00:17:26.960 --> 00:17:29.600
There was no handy at this time.

236
00:17:29.600 --> 00:17:32.080
So we told Śwematajik this story,

237
00:17:32.080 --> 00:17:34.280
and she was just laughing.

238
00:17:34.280 --> 00:17:37.960
And after she told us the meaning of abandon,

239
00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:43.000
she said, you see, when you do this movement in the water,

240
00:17:43.000 --> 00:17:46.640
it's going very deep in the water.

241
00:17:46.640 --> 00:17:51.840
When you do this movement here, and this is the Saṃsāra,

242
00:17:51.840 --> 00:17:54.560
it's going deep in Paramṣaitanya,

243
00:17:54.560 --> 00:17:58.480
who takes over all problems.

244
00:17:58.520 --> 00:18:02.920
The day after this program with Anne-Grédre,

245
00:18:02.920 --> 00:18:06.200
