And don't lose the joy of the connection to the divine.

766
00:51:53.400 --> 00:51:59.200
Meditate, meditate, meditate.

767
00:51:59.240 --> 00:52:06.200
And meditate means to be in the state of thoughtless awareness,

768
00:52:06.200 --> 00:52:12.240
this etheric area where no negativity can penetrate,

769
00:52:12.240 --> 00:52:17.080
where yogis are building an aura of spirituality

770
00:52:17.080 --> 00:52:19.640
around this Earth.

771
00:52:19.640 --> 00:52:22.920
We are her hands.

772
00:52:22.920 --> 00:52:26.360
We are her instruments.

773
00:52:26.360 --> 00:52:30.960
So we should go more and more in this thoughtless awareness

774
00:52:30.960 --> 00:52:36.120
so that her love, her compassion can come on this Earth

775
00:52:36.120 --> 00:52:41.960
and fight negativity wanting to destroy her creation.

776
00:52:41.960 --> 00:52:44.040
Jai Shimataji.
